{"id":"api/common/NgSwitch","title":"NgSwitch","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common/NgSwitch\", \"name\": \"NgSwitch\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/common/src/directives/ng_switch.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L37-L184\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/common/src/directives/ng_switch.ts#L37-L184\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"ngswitch\">NgSwitch<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#ngswitch\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">容器上的 <code>[<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a>]</code> 指令指定要匹配的表示式。匹配的表示式由容器內檢視上的 <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a></code>\n指令提供。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The <code>[<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a>]</code> directive on a container specifies an expression to match against.\nThe expressions to match are provided by <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a></code> directives on views within the container.</p>\n\n\n    <p no-translate=\"\"><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#description\">檢視\"說明\"...</a></p>\n  </section>\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">參見<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><p><code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitchCase</a></code></p></li>\n    <li><p><code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchDefault\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitchDefault</a></code></p></li>\n    <li><p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/structural-directives\">結構型指令</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/structural-directives\">Structural Directives</a></p>\n</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n<h2 id=\"匯出自\">匯出自<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#匯出自\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">CommonModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"selector-list\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">選擇器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a>]</code></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <a name=\"properties\"></a>\n  <h2 id=\"instance-properties\">屬性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#instance-properties\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>屬性</th>\n        <th>說明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"ngSwitch\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"property-binding\">@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</span><br><span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a></span>: any</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <span class=\"write-only-property\">只寫</span>\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n  \n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">如果有匹配項，則渲染匹配的檢視。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Every view that matches is rendered.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">如果沒有匹配項，則渲染 <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchDefault\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchDefault</a></code></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">If there are no matches, a view with the <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchDefault\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchDefault</a></code> directive is rendered.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><code>[<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitch</a>]</code> 陳述式中但任何 <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitchCase</a></code> 或 <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchDefault\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchDefault</a></code> 指令之外的元素都會保留在該位置。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Elements within the <code>[<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitch</a>]</code> statement but outside of any <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitchCase</a></code>\nor <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchDefault\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchDefault</a></code> directive are preserved at the location.</p>\n\n<code-example>\n`[<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitch</a>]` 陳述式內任何除 `<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitchCase</a>` 或 `<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchDefault\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchDefault</a>` 指令之外的元素都保留在原位。\n</code-example>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">為指令定義一個容器元素，並指定要匹配的 switch 表示式作為屬性：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Define a container element for the directive, and specify the switch expression\nto match against as an attribute:</p>\n\n<code-example>\n&lt;container-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a>]=\"switch_expression\"&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在容器內，<code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a></code> 陳述式將匹配表示式指定為屬性。包括用 <code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchDefault\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchDefault</a></code>\n作為最後一種情況。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Within the container, <code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a></code> statements specify the match expressions\nas attributes. Include <code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchDefault\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchDefault</a></code> as the final case.</p>\n\n<code-example>\n&lt;container-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a>]=\"switch_expression\"&gt;\n   &lt;some-element *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a>=\"match_expression_1\"&gt;...&lt;/some-element&gt;\n...\n   &lt;some-element *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchDefault\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchDefault</a>&gt;...&lt;/some-element&gt;\n&lt;/container-element&gt;\n</code-example>\n<h3 id=\"usage-examples\" translation-result=\"on\">使用範例<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#usage-examples\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3><h3 translation-origin=\"off\">Usage Examples<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#usage-examples\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">下面的範例示範如何使用多個分支來顯示同一檢視：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The following example shows how to use more than one case to display the same view:</p>\n\n<code-example>\n&lt;container-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a>]=\"switch_expression\"&gt;\n  &lt;!-- the same view can be shown in more than one case --&gt;\n  &lt;some-element *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a>=\"match_expression_1\"&gt;...&lt;/some-element&gt;\n  &lt;some-element *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a>=\"match_expression_2\"&gt;...&lt;/some-element&gt;\n  &lt;some-other-element *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a>=\"match_expression_3\"&gt;...&lt;/some-other-element&gt;\n  &lt;!--default case when there are no matches --&gt;\n  &lt;some-element *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchDefault\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchDefault</a>&gt;...&lt;/some-element&gt;\n&lt;/container-element&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">以下範例示範如何巢狀(Nesting)案例：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The following example shows how cases can be nested:</p>\n\n<code-example>\n&lt;container-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a>]=\"switch_expression\"&gt;\n      &lt;some-element *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a>=\"match_expression_1\"&gt;...&lt;/some-element&gt;\n      &lt;some-element *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a>=\"match_expression_2\"&gt;...&lt;/some-element&gt;\n      &lt;some-other-element *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a>=\"match_expression_3\"&gt;...&lt;/some-other-element&gt;\n      &lt;ng-container *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a>=\"match_expression_3\"&gt;\n        &lt;!-- use a ng-container to group <a href=\"api/forms/SelectMultipleControlValueAccessor\" class=\"code-anchor\">multiple</a> root nodes --&gt;\n        &lt;inner-element&gt;&lt;/inner-element&gt;\n        &lt;inner-other-element&gt;&lt;/inner-other-element&gt;\n      &lt;/ng-container&gt;\n      &lt;some-element *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchDefault\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchDefault</a>&gt;...&lt;/some-element&gt;\n    &lt;/container-element&gt;\n</code-example>\n\n  </section>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/CommonModule\n - api/common/NgSwitchCase\n - api/common/NgSwitchDefault\n - errors/NG0910\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8103\n - guide/ajs-quick-reference\n - guide/built-in-directives\n - guide/cheatsheet\n - guide/dynamic-form\n - guide/structural-directives\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/CommonModule\n - api/common/NgSwitch#description\n - api/common/NgSwitch#instance-properties\n - api/common/NgSwitch#ngswitch\n - api/common/NgSwitch#see-also\n - api/common/NgSwitch#selectors\n - api/common/NgSwitch#usage-examples\n - api/common/NgSwitch#使用範例\n - api/common/NgSwitch#匯出自\n - api/common/NgSwitchCase\n - api/common/NgSwitchDefault\n - api/core/Input\n - api/forms/SelectMultipleControlValueAccessor\n - guide/structural-directives\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/common/src/directives/ng_switch.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L37-L184\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/common/src/directives/ng_switch.ts#L37-L184\n-->"}